pr_title: Add support of Kotlin/Native and Upgrade Gradle Build System to Kotlin DSL in processing-android
pr_body:
- [x] **Add support of Kotlin in the project**
- [x] **Migrate AR, VR, Core library from Java to Kotlin** 
- [x] **Upgrade Groovy based Gradle to Kotlin DSL based Gradle Build System**
- [x] **Refactor the codebase**
- [x] **Implement migrated code on JVM**
- [x] **Solve some renderer issues**

An outcome of : **_Google Summer of Code 2020_**
Author : Aditya Rana @ranaaditya
Mentor : Syam Sundar K @SyamSundarKirubakaran

pr_title: Add support of Kotlin/Native and Upgrade Gradle Build System to Kotlin DSL in processing-android
pr_body:
- [x] **Add support of Kotlin in the project**
- [x] **Migrate AR, VR, Core library from Java to Kotlin** 
- [x] **Upgrade Groovy based Gradle to Kotlin DSL based Gradle Build System**
- [x] **Refactor the codebase**
- [x] **Implement migrated code on JVM**
- [x] **Solve some renderer issues**

An outcome of : **_Google Summer of Code 2020_**
Author : Aditya Rana @ranaaditya
Mentor : Syam Sundar K @SyamSundarKirubakaran
